    <h3 style="font-weight:bold;"> About me </h3>
    <hr class="solid">
    <h5 style="font-weight:bold;" > Studies and work experience </h5>
    <p>  21 years old student specialized in Computer Science. I am in my last
    year studying Computer Engineering degree at the University of Cádiz </p>
    <p> I have been working in <a href="https://tic145.uca.es/">SIC (Sistemas Inteligentes de la Computación)
    Research Group</a> at the University of Cádiz as a research student for two
    years (2018-2020). SIC's activity is based on artificial intelligence
    projects.</p>
    <p>During my stay, I have been working in the following technologies and algorithms:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Web Scrapping to retrieve data about different football players using
        Python 3 and BeautifulSoup 4.
      </li>
      <li>Sensitive Analysis using R language to study the importance of the
      different LLVM 3.8 Code Optimizations in relation to the execution time.
      </li>
      <li>MonoObjective Genetic Algorithms using R language trying to find the best
      combination of LLVM 3.8 Code Optimizations to improve the execution time.
      </li>
      <li>MonoObjective Genetic Algorithms using JMetalPy framework in Python 3 and
      research about different approaches to manage noise in fitness function.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>I have been working in <a href="https://ucanfly.uca.es/">UCAnFly</a>,
    a space project which aims to build a nanosatellite to explorea the
    feasibility of novel magnetic measurement systems for space missions who required tiny sensors and long integration time, for two years (2018-2020).</p>
            <p>My main tasks when I was inside the team are listed below: </p>
            <ul>
            <li>Software Design for the On Board Software (Flow Diagrams,
              Use-Case Diagrams, Software Test Plan...). </li>
            <li>Software Repository and baseline/release system designed</li>
            <li> TMS570LS0714 MCU programming using C with Code Composer Studio
              and HALCoGen Software.</li>
            </ul>
    <hr class = "solid">
    <h5 style="font-weight:bold;"> Skills </h5>
    <ul>
      <li> C/C++ advanced knowledge. Experience with multimedia libraries, for
        example, SDL. Experience with C for Embedded Systems. </li>
      <li>Advanced knowledge about LLVM compiler infrastructure and code
        compiling optimization tools.</li>
      <li> Python 3 advanced knowledge. Experience with Machine Learning
        libraries (Sklearn, Scipy...) and Desktop UID libraries (Kivy, PyQt).</li>
      <li>Advanced knowledge of MatLab. Experience making machine learning
        algorithms (Classifiers, regression...), voice recognition
        techniques(DTW), image recognition techniques and optimization
        algorithms such as PSO(Particle Swarm Optimization) and MonoObjective
        Genetic Algorithms.</li>
      <li>R language knowledge about sensitive analysis, genetic algorithms and
        parallel functions.</li>
      <li>Medium knowledge about Java and Golang. Experience using Desktop UID
      libraries with Golang using Fyne.io</li>
      <li>API REST developer experience using Python (Bottle framework or Flash) or
        Go(Gin-Gonic).</li>
      <li>Backend experience with Laravel.</li>
      <li>Frontend experience with Bootstrap 4 and JQuery.</li>
    </ul>
